  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Desktop Pals is the ultimate desktop companion game. The game has a wide selection of pets to chose from, and features such as game overlay; you will never have to leave your new pal!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614720/extras/e160270c5f9f20eb6657d1d63f4d5e92.poster.avif?t=1743508843\" width=800 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614720/extras/e160270c5f9f20eb6657d1d63f4d5e92.webm?t=1743508843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614720/extras/e160270c5f9f20eb6657d1d63f4d5e92.mp4?t=1743508843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features several artstyles, so you can chose which one you prefer. The pets include dogs, cats, a wolf, a panda, rabbits, a hedgehog, and more. It's a real zoo in here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The pals are interactive! Each pal has a unique reaction to you petting him, and they have natural behaviour patterns, such as falling asleep or going for a walk around your screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614720/extras/9b3c513300287cf95ceebce0ab085f10.poster.avif?t=1743508843\" width=800 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614720/extras/9b3c513300287cf95ceebce0ab085f10.webm?t=1743508843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614720/extras/9b3c513300287cf95ceebce0ab085f10.mp4?t=1743508843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Desktop Pals also works over most modern games, so you can play with your pal during those pesky down-times, like when you are waiting for your friend to join your lobby.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game also features advanced customization. You can choose the pals location on your screen, his scale, his capabilities, and more! You can change the game to your liking.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Desktop Pals is the ultimate desktop companion game. The game has a wide selection of pets to chose from, and features such as game overlay; you will never have to leave your new pal!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614720/extras/e160270c5f9f20eb6657d1d63f4d5e92.poster.avif?t=1743508843\" width=800 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614720/extras/e160270c5f9f20eb6657d1d63f4d5e92.webm?t=1743508843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614720/extras/e160270c5f9f20eb6657d1d63f4d5e92.mp4?t=1743508843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game features several artstyles, so you can chose which one you prefer. The pets include dogs, cats, a wolf, a panda, rabbits, a hedgehog, and more. It's a real zoo in here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The pals are interactive! Each pal has a unique reaction to you petting him, and they have natural behaviour patterns, such as falling asleep or going for a walk around your screen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614720/extras/9b3c513300287cf95ceebce0ab085f10.poster.avif?t=1743508843\" width=800 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614720/extras/9b3c513300287cf95ceebce0ab085f10.webm?t=1743508843\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614720/extras/9b3c513300287cf95ceebce0ab085f10.mp4?t=1743508843\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Desktop Pals also 